3. cs.LG - The paper discusses machine learning techniques used in subgame solving, which is a core topic in this sub-category. 
4. cs.CR - The paper discusses security and safety concerns in subgame solving, which is a core topic in this sub-category. 
5. cs.SY - The paper discusses how subgame solving can be repeated as the game progresses, which is a topic related to control systems and decision-making in this sub-category.
